! version = 2.0

// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  TalkPrep Brain — persona: talkprep
//
//  Design:
//    - Simple informational intents return STATIC text (Option B — no HTTP)
//    - Operations that need the database use <call>tool</call> macros
//    - Substitutions in global.rive translate Haitian Creole BEFORE matching
//    - All stages inherit from 'random' which has the base + AI fallback
//
//  Substitution reference (from global.rive):
//    montre → show | mwen → my | ki → what | anmwey/ede → help
//    piblikasyon → publications | pratike → practice | ekspòte → export
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

// ── topic random (base — always available) ───────────────────────────
> topic random

  // ── Help (static text — no gateway needed) ──

  + help
  - 📚 *TalkPrep commands available:*\n\n• *show my talks* — list your talks\n• *status* — see your progress\n• *show publications* — browse source material\n• *import talk [topic name]* — start a new talk\n• *develop section [name]* — write a section (AI)\n• *evaluate talk* — score your talk (AI)\n• *rehearsal* — coaching tips (AI)\n• *export* — generate final manuscript\n• *cost* — view token usage

  + what can you do
  @ help

  // ── Status / show talks (static prompt — gateway fills details) ──
  // NOTE: substitution turns "montre talk mwen" → "show talk my"
  // These triggers cover the most common phrasings.

  + status
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  + show [my] talks
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  + show [my] talk
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  + show talk my
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  + list [my] talks
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  + my talks
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  + what [are] my talks
  - <call>talkmaster_status</call>

  // ── Publications (static — no DB needed) ──

  + show publications
  - <call>list_publications</call>

  + list publications
  - <call>list_publications</call>

  + what [are the] (books|publications|pubs)
  - <call>list_publications</call>

  // ── Topics for a publication ──

  + list topics *
  - <call>list_topics <star></call>

  + topics [in] *
  - <call>list_topics <star></call>

  // ── Cost report ──

  + (cost|usage|tokens)
  - <call>cost_report</call>

  + how much [have i spent]
  - <call>cost_report</call>

  // ── AI fallback — explicit delegation to LangGraph ──

  + *
  - {{ai_fallback}}

< topic

// ── Stage 1: Import ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
> topic stage_1 inherits random

  + import talk *
  - <call>import_talk <star></call>

  + import *
  - <call>import_talk <star></call>

  + start [a] [new] talk [about] *
  - <call>import_talk <star></call>

  + select talk *
  - <call>select_active_talk <star></call>

  + (use|switch to) talk *
  - <call>select_active_talk <star></call>

< topic

// ── Stage 2: Revision ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
> topic stage_2 inherits stage_1

  + (create|new) revision *
  - <call>create_revision <star></call>

  + revision *
  - <call>create_revision <star></call>

  + revise *
  - <call>create_revision <star></call>

< topic

// ── Stage 3: Development ──────────────────────────────────────────────
> topic stage_3 inherits stage_2

  + develop [section] *
  - <call>develop_section <star></call>

  + write [section] *
  - <call>develop_section <star></call>

  + generate [section] *
  - <call>develop_section <star></call>

< topic

// ── Stage 4: Evaluation ───────────────────────────────────────────────
> topic stage_4 inherits stage_3

  + evaluate [talk]
  - <call>evaluate_talk</call>

  + evaluate [my] talk
  - <call>evaluate_talk</call>

  + (scores|score|results) [for] *
  - <call>get_evaluation_scores <star></call>

  + (scores|score|results)
  - <call>get_evaluation_scores</call>

< topic

// ── Stage 5: Rehearsal ────────────────────────────────────────────────
> topic stage_5 inherits stage_4

  + (rehearsal|rehearse|practice) [*]
  - <call>rehearsal_cue <star></call>

  + (cues|coaching|tips) [for] *
  - <call>rehearsal_cue <star></call>

< topic

// ── Stage 6: Export ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
> topic stage_6 inherits stage_5

  + (export|print|final|manuscript) [*]
  - <call>export_talk_summary <star></call>

< topic
